## Report schema
```yaml
tool: "<tool + version>"
command: "<exact invocation>"
whole_codebase: { lines: <n>, covered: <n>, pct: <float> }
change_surface: { lines: <n>, covered: <n>, pct: <float> }
uncovered:
  - location: "<path:line>"
    disposition: add-test | justified-exclusion
    reason: "<if excluded>"
delta_vs_baseline: <+/-float>
verdict: pass | changes-requested | blocked
```

## Gap report
List every uncovered region on the change surface, grouped by disposition.
A `blocked` verdict requires at least one `add-test` row; `pass` requires
zero `add-test` rows plus an affirmative delta.

```yaml
gaps:
  - location: "<path:line-range>"
    disposition: add-test
    risk: "<why untested behavior is reachable in prod>"
    proposed_test: "<unit | integration | e2e>"
  - location: "<path:line-range>"
    disposition: justified-exclusion
    kind: unreachable | trivial-wrapper | generated
    citation: "<file:line that proves the kind>"
end_to_end_gaps:
  - boundary: "<service/process crossed>"
    why_unit_only_is_insufficient: "<behavior that only e2e catches>"
delta_direction: up | flat | down
```
